HEADWORD: Bookstand
<hw>Book"stand`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
place or stand for the sale of books in the streets; a
bookstall.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A stand to hold books for reading or
reference.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bookstore</ent>⟦br⟧
